  </sponsors>
  <source>Institut de Cancérologie de Lorraine</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to identify in patients with brain metastases the predictive factors of overall
      survival, survival without local recurrence and survival with progression-free brain
      metastases after complementary whole brain radiotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
